{"ID":"20220906203933-5y6vg7g","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906203933-5y6vg7g","title":"c-1计算机网络","type":"doc","updated":"20220906203933"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203934-341g06x","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20220906203934-341g06x","updated":"20220906203934"}},{"ID":"20220906203935-ctsche1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203935-ctsche1","updated":"20220906203935"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. 计算机基础","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203936-ap0j4yq","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906203936-ap0j4yq","updated":"20220906203936"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906203937-i1v7yen","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203937-i1v7yen","updated":"20220906203937"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/","TextMarkTextContent":"JavaGuide"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：「Java学习+面试指南」一份涵盖大部分 Java 程序员所需要掌握的核心知识。准备 Java 面试，首选 JavaGuide！","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203938-o0tj5k3","Type":"NodeHTMLBlock","Data":"\u003cdiv align=\"center\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://www.yuque.com/docs/share/8a30ffb5-83f3-40f9-baf9-38de68b906dc\"\u003e\n            \u003cimg src=\"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/xingqiu/xingqiu.png\" style=\"margin: 0 auto; width: 850px;\" /\u003e\n        \u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/Snailclimb/JavaGuide-Interview\"\u003eGithub\u003c/a\u003e |\n        \u003ca href=\"https://gitee.com/SnailClimb/JavaGuide-Interview\"\u003eGitee\u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/p\u003e  \n\u003c/div\u003e","HtmlBlockType":6,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203938-o0tj5k3","updated":"20220906203938"}},{"ID":"20220906203939-ymhlal9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203939-ymhlal9","updated":"20220906203939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.1 计算机网络","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203940-pcdijj2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203940-pcdijj2","updated":"20220906203940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OSI 七层模型是什么？每一层的作用是什么？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203941-7pzf900","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203941-7pzf900","updated":"20220906203941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"OSI 七层模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是国际标准化组织提出一个网络分层模型，其大体结构以及每一层提供的功能如下图所示：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203942-sl0ojt1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203942-sl0ojt1","updated":"20220906203942"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"OSI 七层模型","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/cs-basics/network/osi-7-model.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203943-y1e7to1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203943-y1e7to1","updated":"20220906203943"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"每一层都专注做一件事情，并且每一层都需要使用下一层提供的功能比如传输层需要使用网络层提供的路由和寻址功能，这样传输层才知道把数据传输到哪里去。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203944-mjltkb7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203944-mjltkb7","updated":"20220906203944"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"OSI 的七层体系结构概念清楚，理论也很完整，但是它比较复杂而且不实用，而且有些功能在多个层中重复出现。"}]},{"ID":"20220906203945-7rjpdoo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203945-7rjpdoo","updated":"20220906203945"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上面这种图可能比较抽象，再来一个比较生动的图片。下面这个图片是我在国外的一个网站上看到的，非常赞！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203946-7wxz63x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203946-7wxz63x","updated":"20220906203946"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"osi七层模型2","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/osi七层模型2.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203947-kei3r7q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203947-kei3r7q","updated":"20220906203947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"既然 OSI 七层模型这么厉害，为什么干不过 TCP/IP 四 层模型呢？"}]},{"ID":"20220906203948-lq6m71h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203948-lq6m71h","updated":"20220906203948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的确，OSI 七层模型当时一直被一些大公司甚至一些国家政府支持。这样的背景下，为什么会失败呢？我觉得主要有下面几方面原因：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203949-j5dv0jl","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203949-j5dv0jl","updated":"20220906203949"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203950-t4y68sl","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203950-t4y68sl","updated":"20220906203950"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203951-0glfxwd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203951-0glfxwd","updated":"20220906203951"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OSI 的专家缺乏实际经验，他们在完成 OSI 标准时缺乏商业驱动力","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203952-7mh0av3","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203952-7mh0av3","updated":"20220906203952"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203953-adt3h0e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203953-adt3h0e","updated":"20220906203953"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OSI 的协议实现起来过分复杂，而且运行效率很低","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203954-kcitlct","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203954-kcitlct","updated":"20220906203954"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203955-ke77ayo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203955-ke77ayo","updated":"20220906203955"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OSI 制定标准的周期太长，因而使得按 OSI 标准生产的设备无法及时进入市场（20 世纪 90 年代初期，虽然整套的 OSI 国际标准都已经制定出来，但基于 TCP/IP 的互联网已经抢先在全球相当大的范围成功运行了）","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203956-d899yez","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NA==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203956-d899yez","updated":"20220906203956"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203957-tcbzw6m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203957-tcbzw6m","updated":"20220906203957"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OSI 的层次划分不太合理，有些功能在多个层次中重复出现。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203958-rkx1xnq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203958-rkx1xnq","updated":"20220906203958"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OSI 七层模型虽然失败了，但是却提供了很多不错的理论基础。为了更好地去了解网络分层，OSI 七层模型还是非常有必要学习的。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203959-js7pacf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203959-js7pacf","updated":"20220906203959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最后再分享一个关于 OSI 七层模型非常不错的总结图片！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203960-xmvz83e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203960-xmvz83e","updated":"20220906203960"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/cs-basics/network/osi-model-detail.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203961-3j09baz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203961-3j09baz","updated":"20220906203961"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TCP/IP 四层模型是什么？每一层的作用是什么？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203962-mybn7rs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203962-mybn7rs","updated":"20220906203962"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"TCP/IP 四层模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是目前被广泛采用的一种模型,我们可以将 TCP / IP 模型看作是 OSI 七层模型的精简版本，由以下 4 层组成：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203963-g5sbuqf","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203963-g5sbuqf","updated":"20220906203963"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203964-y5ky6n8","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203964-y5ky6n8","updated":"20220906203964"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203965-2mydsxp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203965-2mydsxp","updated":"20220906203965"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应用层","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203966-kcve8db","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203966-kcve8db","updated":"20220906203966"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203967-xde1tse","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203967-xde1tse","updated":"20220906203967"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"传输层","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203968-fr1t6nn","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203968-fr1t6nn","updated":"20220906203968"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203969-zqvfgch","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203969-zqvfgch","updated":"20220906203969"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"网络层","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203970-e2zm78i","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NA==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203970-e2zm78i","updated":"20220906203970"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203971-svuyke1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203971-svuyke1","updated":"20220906203971"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"网络接口层","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203972-myb051w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203972-myb051w","updated":"20220906203972"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需要注意的是，我们并不能将 TCP/IP 四层模型 和 OSI 七层模型完全精确地匹配起来，不过可以简单将两者对应起来，如下图所示：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203973-b9l9fjn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203973-b9l9fjn","updated":"20220906203973"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"TCP/IP 四层模型","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/cs-basics/network/tcp-ip-4-model.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203974-56jynj8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203974-56jynj8","updated":"20220906203974"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应用层（Application layer）","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203975-b58sqju","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203975-b58sqju","updated":"20220906203975"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"应用层位于传输层之上，主要提供两个终端设备上的应用程序之间信息交换的服务，它定义了信息交换的格式，消息会交给下一层传输层来传输。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 我们把应用层交互的数据单元称为报文。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203976-nwfkp14","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203976-nwfkp14","updated":"20220906203976"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/5971-2-7I1-20220111095024771-20220111201807861.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203977-wrgn3ga","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203977-wrgn3ga","updated":"20220906203977"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应用层协议定义了网络通信规则，对于不同的网络应用需要不同的应用层协议。在互联网中应用层协议很多，如支持 Web 应用的 HTTP 协议，支持电子邮件的 SMTP 协议等等。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203978-2lz16ld","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203978-2lz16ld","updated":"20220906203978"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"应用层重要协议","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/cs-basics/network/application-layer-protocol.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203979-z57ina1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203979-z57ina1","updated":"20220906203979"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应用层常见协议总结，请看这篇文章：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/cs-basics/network/application-layer-protocol.html","TextMarkTextContent":"应用层常见协议总结（应用层）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203980-qumaok2","Type":"NodeHTMLBlock","Data":"\u003cdiv align=\"center\"\u003e   \n    \u003cimg src=\"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/gongzhonghaoxuanchuan.png\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;\" /\u003e  \n\u003c/div\u003e","HtmlBlockType":6,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203980-qumaok2","updated":"20220906203980"}},{"ID":"20220906203981-xsm8qju","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203981-xsm8qju","updated":"20220906203981"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"传输层（Transport layer）","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203982-psdrzsb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203982-psdrzsb","updated":"20220906203982"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"传输层的主要任务就是负责向两台终端设备进程之间的通信提供通用的数据传输服务。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 应用进程利用该服务传送应用层报文。“通用的”是指并不针对某一个特定的网络应用，而是多种应用可以使用同一个运输层服务。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203983-cvrd363","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203983-cvrd363","updated":"20220906203983"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"运输层主要使用以下两种协议："}]},{"ID":"20220906203984-4uz5r4e","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203984-4uz5r4e","updated":"20220906203984"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203985-kvb37jt","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203985-kvb37jt","updated":"20220906203985"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203986-elwkxfr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203986-elwkxfr","updated":"20220906203986"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"传输控制协议 TCP"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（Transmisson Control Protocol）--提供 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"面向连接"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"可靠的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 数据传输服务。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203987-2asnl45","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203987-2asnl45","updated":"20220906203987"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203988-nkkfaqg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203988-nkkfaqg","updated":"20220906203988"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"用户数据协议 UDP"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（User Datagram Protocol）--提供 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"无连接"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的，尽最大努力的数据传输服务（不保证数据传输的可靠性）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203989-7cle6jx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203989-7cle6jx","updated":"20220906203989"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"传输层重要协议","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/cs-basics/network/transport-layer-protocol.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203990-gumjdqe","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203990-gumjdqe","updated":"20220906203990"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"网络层（Network layer）","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203991-b3bu68s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203991-b3bu68s","updated":"20220906203991"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"网络层负责为分组交换网上的不同主机提供通信服务。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 在发送数据时，网络层把运输层产生的报文段或用户数据报封装成分组和包进行传送。在 TCP/IP 体系结构中，由于网络层使用 IP 协议，因此分组也叫 IP 数据报，简称数据报。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203992-2wwxprl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203992-2wwxprl","updated":"20220906203992"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⚠️注意 ：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不要把运输层的“用户数据报 UDP”和网络层的“IP 数据报”弄混"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203993-5o3cee5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203993-5o3cee5","updated":"20220906203993"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"网络层的还有一个任务就是选择合适的路由，使源主机运输层所传下来的分组，能通过网络层中的路由器找到目的主机。"}]},{"ID":"20220906203994-mh8m9qh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203994-mh8m9qh","updated":"20220906203994"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这里强调指出，网络层中的“网络”二字已经不是我们通常谈到的具体网络，而是指计算机网络体系结构模型中第三层的名称。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203995-2qafrhg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203995-2qafrhg","updated":"20220906203995"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"互联网是由大量的异构（heterogeneous）网络通过路由器（router）相互连接起来的。互联网使用的网络层协议是无连接的网际协议（Intert Prococol）和许多路由选择协议，因此互联网的网络层也叫做 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"网际层"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 或 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"IP 层"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203996-gkr6cx1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203996-gkr6cx1","updated":"20220906203996"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"网络层重要协议","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/cs-basics/network/nerwork-layer-protocol.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203997-1bnl6vo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203997-1bnl6vo","updated":"20220906203997"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"网络层常见协议"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203998-u3o5zen","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203998-u3o5zen","updated":"20220906203998"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203999-z2ugktw","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203999-z2ugktw","updated":"20220906203999"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204000-frh5ozu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204000-frh5ozu","updated":"20220906204000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"IP:网际协议"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：网际协议 IP 是TCP/IP协议中最重要的协议之一，也是网络层最重要的协议之一，IP协议的作用包括寻址规约、定义数据包的格式等等，是网络层信息传输的主力协议。目前IP协议主要分为两种，一种是过去的IPv4，另一种是较新的IPv6，目前这两种协议都在使用，但后者已经被提议来取代前者。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204001-jjaru2o","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204001-jjaru2o","updated":"20220906204001"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204002-u9mjf6q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204002-u9mjf6q","updated":"20220906204002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"ARP 协议"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：ARP协议，全称地址解析协议（Address Resolution Protocol），它解决的是网络层地址和链路层地址之间的转换问题。因为一个IP数据报在物理上传输的过程中，总是需要知道下一跳（物理上的下一个目的地）该去往何处，但IP地址属于逻辑地址，而MAC地址才是物理地址，ARP协议解决了IP地址转MAC地址的一些问题。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204003-6bqzvsx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204003-6bqzvsx","updated":"20220906204003"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204004-enkb07a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204004-enkb07a","updated":"20220906204004"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"NAT:网络地址转换协议"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：NAT协议（Network Address Translation）的应用场景如同它的名称——网络地址转换，应用于内部网到外部网的地址转换过程中。具体地说，在一个小的子网（局域网，LAN）内，各主机使用的是同一个LAN下的IP地址，但在该LAN以外，在广域网（WAN）中，需要一个统一的IP地址来标识该LAN在整个Internet上的位置。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204005-jtd75qe","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204005-jtd75qe","updated":"20220906204005"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204006-noz092y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204006-noz092y","updated":"20220906204006"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"......","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204007-h6wz0cv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204007-h6wz0cv","updated":"20220906204007"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"网络接口层（Network interface layer）","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204008-vdstcdy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204008-vdstcdy","updated":"20220906204008"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们可以把网络接口层看作是数据链路层和物理层的合体。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204009-c2txqlu","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204009-c2txqlu","updated":"20220906204009"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204010-1nl6g9e","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204010-1nl6g9e","updated":"20220906204010"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204011-d0h5wyz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204011-d0h5wyz","updated":"20220906204011"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据链路层(data link layer)通常简称为链路层（ 两台主机之间的数据传输，总是在一段一段的链路上传送的）。","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"数据链路层的作用是将网络层交下来的 IP 数据报组装成帧，在两个相邻节点间的链路上传送帧。每一帧包括数据和必要的控制信息（如同步信息，地址信息，差错控制等）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204012-aa7qsja","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204012-aa7qsja","updated":"20220906204012"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204013-mec30nv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204013-mec30nv","updated":"20220906204013"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"物理层的作用是实现相邻计算机节点之间比特流的透明传送，尽可能屏蔽掉具体传输介质和物理设备的差异"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204014-m3t22sk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204014-m3t22sk","updated":"20220906204014"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"网络接口层重要协议","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/cs-basics/network/network-interface-layer-protocol.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204015-527idy2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204015-527idy2","updated":"20220906204015"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204016-55vk8e9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204016-55vk8e9","updated":"20220906204016"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简单总结一下每一层包含的协议和核心技术:","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204017-j9rqqgw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204017-j9rqqgw","updated":"20220906204017"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"TCP/IP 各层协议概览","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/cs-basics/network/network-protocol-overview.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204018-xd5hi08","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204018-xd5hi08","updated":"20220906204018"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"应用层协议"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" :","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204019-tf1ljvr","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204019-tf1ljvr","updated":"20220906204019"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204020-uu9mct5","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204020-uu9mct5","updated":"20220906204020"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204021-xzj4mva","Type":"NodeParagraph","