码用于描述 HTTP 请求的结果，比如2xx 就代表请求被成功处理。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204201-63qzcx5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204201-63qzcx5","updated":"20220906204201"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"HTTP 状态码","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://my-blog-to-use.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019/7/状态码.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204202-vw2okve","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204202-vw2okve","updated":"20220906204202"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关于 HTTP 状态码更详细的总结，可以看我写的这篇文章：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/cs-basics/network/http-status-codes.html","TextMarkTextContent":"HTTP 常见状态码总结（应用层）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204203-vv9xe76","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204203-vv9xe76","updated":"20220906204203"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"HTTP 和 HTTPS 有什么区别？（重要）","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204204-n2a5mkn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204204-n2a5mkn","updated":"20220906204204"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204205-0a6w2qm","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204205-0a6w2qm","updated":"20220906204205"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204206-qqsuoue","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204206-qqsuoue","updated":"20220906204206"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"端口号"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：HTTP 默认是 80，HTTPS 默认是 443。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204207-ep6plkn","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204207-ep6plkn","updated":"20220906204207"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204208-2f665pi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204208-2f665pi","updated":"20220906204208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"URL 前缀"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：HTTP 的 URL 前缀是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"http://"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，HTTPS 的 URL 前缀是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"https://"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204209-20hluv1","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204209-20hluv1","updated":"20220906204209"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204210-4uemqz3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204210-4uemqz3","updated":"20220906204210"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"安全性和资源消耗"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ： HTTP 协议运行在 TCP 之上，所有传输的内容都是明文，客户端和服务器端都无法验证对方的身份。HTTPS 是运行在 SSL/TLS 之上的 HTTP 协议，SSL/TLS 运行在 TCP 之上。所有传输的内容都经过加密，加密采用对称加密，但对称加密的密钥用服务器方的证书进行了非对称加密。所以说，HTTP 安全性没有 HTTPS 高，但是 HTTPS 比 HTTP 耗费更多服务器资源。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204211-2zherrj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204211-2zherrj","updated":"20220906204211"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关于 HTTP 和 HTTPS 更详细的对比总结，可以看我写的这篇文章：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/cs-basics/network/http\u0026https.html","TextMarkTextContent":"HTTP vs HTTPS（应用层）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204212-i7hi9fg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204212-i7hi9fg","updated":"20220906204212"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"HTTP 1.0 和 HTTP 1.1 有什么区别？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204213-jofqq0v","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204213-jofqq0v","updated":"20220906204213"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204214-xxxwf80","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204214-xxxwf80","updated":"20220906204214"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204215-q5ob1e6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204215-q5ob1e6","updated":"20220906204215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"连接方式"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : HTTP 1.0 为短连接，HTTP 1.1 支持长连接。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204216-3udc5wp","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204216-3udc5wp","updated":"20220906204216"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204217-v8vl0i9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204217-v8vl0i9","updated":"20220906204217"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"状态响应码"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : HTTP/1.1中新加入了大量的状态码，光是错误响应状态码就新增了24种。比如说，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"100 (Continue)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"——在请求大资源前的预热请求，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"206 (Partial Content)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"——范围请求的标识码，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"409 (Conflict)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"——请求与当前资源的规定冲突，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"410 (Gone)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"——资源已被永久转移，而且没有任何已知的转发地址。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204218-yogffht","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204218-yogffht","updated":"20220906204218"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204219-cbvfpig","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204219-cbvfpig","updated":"20220906204219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"缓存处理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : 在 HTTP1.0 中主要使用 header 里的 If-Modified-Since,Expires 来做为缓存判断的标准，HTTP1.1 则引入了更多的缓存控制策略例如 Entity tag，If-Unmodified-Since, If-Match, If-None-Match 等更多可供选择的缓存头来控制缓存策略。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204220-zlul7qy","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204220-zlul7qy","updated":"20220906204220"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204221-h5if5r4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204221-h5if5r4","updated":"20220906204221"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"带宽优化及网络连接的使用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" :HTTP1.0 中，存在一些浪费带宽的现象，例如客户端只是需要某个对象的一部分，而服务器却将整个对象送过来了，并且不支持断点续传功能，HTTP1.1 则在请求头引入了 range 头域，它允许只请求资源的某个部分，即返回码是 206（Partial Content），这样就方便了开发者自由的选择以便于充分利用带宽和连接。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204222-c276izq","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204222-c276izq","updated":"20220906204222"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204223-cz2ygc0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204223-cz2ygc0","updated":"20220906204223"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Host头处理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : HTTP/1.1在请求头中加入了","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Host"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"字段。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204224-bqpi1vt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204224-bqpi1vt","updated":"20220906204224"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关于 HTTP 1.0 和 HTTP 1.1 更详细的对比总结，可以看我写的这篇文章：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/cs-basics/network/http1.0\u0026http1.1.html","TextMarkTextContent":"HTTP 1.0 vs HTTP 1.1（应用层）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204225-qbynogg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204225-qbynogg","updated":"20220906204225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"HTTP 是不保存状态的协议, 如何保存用户状态?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204226-uzn93z4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204226-uzn93z4","updated":"20220906204226"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"HTTP 是一种不保存状态，即无状态（stateless）协议。也就是说 HTTP 协议自身不对请求和响应之间的通信状态进行保存。那么我们保存用户状态呢？Session 机制的存在就是为了解决这个问题，Session 的主要作用就是通过服务端记录用户的状态。典型的场景是购物车，当你要添加商品到购物车的时候，系统不知道是哪个用户操作的，因为 HTTP 协议是无状态的。服务端给特定的用户创建特定的 Session 之后就可以标识这个用户并且跟踪这个用户了（一般情况下，服务器会在一定时间内保存这个 Session，过了时间限制，就会销毁这个 Session）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204227-7fyxyf0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204227-7fyxyf0","updated":"20220906204227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在服务端保存 Session 的方法很多，最常用的就是内存和数据库(比如是使用内存数据库 redis 保存)。既然 Session 存放在服务器端，那么我们如何实现 Session 跟踪呢？大部分情况下，我们都是通过在 Cookie 中附加一个 Session ID 来方式来跟踪。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204228-sap3mh3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204228-sap3mh3","updated":"20220906204228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Cookie 被禁用怎么办?"}]},{"ID":"20220906204229-o4u2ass","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204229-o4u2ass","updated":"20220906204229"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最常用的就是利用 URL 重写把 Session ID 直接附加在 URL 路径的后面。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204230-el7kntn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204230-el7kntn","updated":"20220906204230"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"HTTP是无状态协议","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://my-blog-to-use.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019-6/HTTP是无状态的.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204231-11xyvgm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204231-11xyvgm","updated":"20220906204231"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"URI 和 URL 的区别是什么?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204232-c5hhqey","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":42,"Padding":2,"Marker":"Kg==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204232-c5hhqey","updated":"20220906204232"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204233-irb5s28","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"*","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":42,"Padding":2,"Marker":"Kg==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204233-irb5s28","updated":"20220906204233"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204234-e6jswwr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204234-e6jswwr","updated":"20220906204234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"URI(Uniform Resource Identifier) 是统一资源标志符，可以唯一标识一个资源。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204235-3lph1me","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"*","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":42,"Padding":2,"Marker":"Kg==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204235-3lph1me","updated":"20220906204235"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204236-j2ftda2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204236-j2ftda2","updated":"20220906204236"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"URL(Uniform Resource Locator) 是统一资源定位符，可以提供该资源的路径。它是一种具体的 URI，即 URL 可以用来标识一个资源，而且还指明了如何 locate 这个资源。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204237-h034sjy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204237-h034sjy","updated":"20220906204237"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"URI 的作用像身份证号一样，URL 的作用更像家庭住址一样。URL 是一种具体的 URI，它不仅唯一标识资源，而且还提供了定位该资源的信息。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204238-vif25f1","Type":"NodeHTMLBlock","Data":"\u003cdiv align=\"center\"\u003e   \n    \u003cimg src=\"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/gongzhonghaoxuanchuan.png\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;\" /\u003e  \n\u003c/div\u003e","HtmlBlockType":6,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204238-vif25f1","updated":"20220906204238"}}]}